1604
01:20:10,405 --> 01:20:11,606
Over.

1605
01:20:11,606 --> 01:20:12,908
- Tell me that I didn't
lose the best friend

1606
01:20:12,908 --> 01:20:13,875
that I've ever had.

1607
01:20:15,043 --> 01:20:16,545
- [Jack] I'm here.

1608
01:20:18,947 --> 01:20:22,951
- Tell me that I can find
a cure before he dies.

1609
01:20:27,055 --> 01:20:28,657
- God, how are ya?

1610
01:20:28,657 --> 01:20:29,491
- [Mike] Good man.

1611
01:20:29,491 --> 01:20:30,725
- You look great man.

1612
01:20:30,725 --> 01:20:32,661
- It's good to see you!
- Good to see you too.

1613
01:20:32,661 --> 01:20:34,062
- [Mike] Okay.

1614
