Yeah, no, I've got
that, I've got that.

1615
01:20:36,898 --> 01:20:38,066
Right, right.

1616
01:20:39,334 --> 01:20:40,302
But does this particular drug

1617
01:20:40,302 --> 01:20:41,570
work on the immune system?

1618
01:20:41,570 --> 01:20:42,404
- [Man On Phone]
Well, it's looking

1619
01:20:42,404 --> 01:20:43,505
very very pleasant.

1620
01:20:43,505 --> 01:20:44,906
- Okay good.

1621
01:20:44,906 --> 01:20:49,277
- No, no, it's Adenocarcinoma.
