even when he should be resting.

1635
01:21:28,884 --> 01:21:30,118
- [Reporter] Mr. Landon,
one more time please.

1636
01:21:30,118 --> 01:21:32,053
- Your Dad belongs to the world.

1637
01:21:33,521 --> 01:21:34,322
Always has.

1638
01:21:37,125 --> 01:21:38,994
- I'm losing my Father.

1639
01:21:38,994 --> 01:21:40,528
- [Michael] That's
enough, thanks.

1640
01:21:40,528 --> 01:21:41,329
- And I haven't even really
- Thanks for coming out.

1641
01:21:41,329 --> 01:21:42,264
- [Mike] found him yet.

1642
01:21:42,264 --> 01:21:42,998
- [Michael] Appreciate it.

1643
