(crowd shouting)

1685
01:24:53,288 --> 01:24:54,122
- Dad?

1686
01:24:56,091 --> 01:24:57,625
Dad!

1687
01:24:57,625 --> 01:24:59,794
- [Michael] Thanks for
coming out, I appreciate it!

1688
01:24:59,794 --> 01:25:00,595
- Dad!

1689
01:25:01,796 --> 01:25:03,264
Dad!

1690
01:25:03,264 --> 01:25:04,099
Daddy!

1691
01:25:05,066 --> 01:25:07,268
Dad, where are you!

1692
01:25:07,268 --> 01:25:08,736
Dad!

1693
01:25:08,736 --> 01:25:09,571
Daddy!

1694
01:25:13,141 --> 01:25:14,809
Leave him alone!

1695
01:25:14,809 --> 01:25:16,144
He's just a man!

1696
01:25:17,045 --> 01:25:18,046
He's my Dad!

1697
01:25:18,880 --> 01:25:21,616
(metal clanking)

1698
01:25:27,555 --> 01:25:30,225
(ambient music)

1699
01:25:31,159 --> 01:25:33,761
(solemn music)

