- [Man] He's gonna pull through!

1706
01:26:34,822 --> 01:26:36,457
He can make it!

1707
01:26:36,457 --> 01:26:37,625
Don't give up!

1708
01:26:52,840 --> 01:26:56,377
- Hey Dad, I've been doing
some research on my own.

1709
01:26:57,612 --> 01:26:59,814
This drug is being
used in Mexico

1710
01:26:59,814 --> 01:27:01,049
with amazing results.

1711
01:27:02,283 --> 01:27:03,551
- Everybody's got a cure.

1712
01:27:04,919 --> 01:27:07,622
Son, do you have any
idea how many people have

1713
01:27:07,622 --> 01:27:08,690
written me this week?

1714
01:27:10,091 --> 01:27:11,459
- No, I mean, I understand.

1715
01:27:13,494 --> 01:27:14,929
- It's all right.

1716
01:27:17,265 --> 01:27:18,166
Let's take a walk.

1717
01:27:22,670 --> 01:27:25,073
Son, I appreciate you
bringing the medicine.

1718
01:27:26,207 --> 01:27:28,309
You gotta know, I got
a medicine cabinet

1719
01:27:28,309 --> 01:27:30,745
full of miracle
cures from Mexico.

1720
01:27:30,745 --> 01:27:31,746
It's not gonna work.

1721
01:27:34,382 --> 01:27:35,183
Sit down.

1722
01:27:36,184 --> 01:27:37,085
Come on, sit down.

1723
01:27:40,121 --> 01:27:41,055
The light's pretty
here isn't it?

1724
01:27:41,055 --> 01:27:42,290
- [Mike] Yeah, it's nice.

1725
01:27:42,290 --> 01:27:43,491
- It's my favorite spot.

1726
01:27:50,832 --> 01:27:52,700
- You've lost more weight Dad.

1727
01:27:52,700 --> 01:27:53,501
- Yeah.

1728
01:27:55,803 --> 01:27:57,805
The tumor's grown to
twice the size Son.

1729
01:28:01,943 --> 01:28:03,177
It won't be long now.

1730
01:28:05,213 --> 01:28:06,147
- Dad--

1731
01:28:06,147 --> 01:28:08,116
- Now look Son, I'm not afraid.

1732
01:28:08,116 --> 01:28:11,252
You know, I'm not
afraid to die Michael,

1733
01:28:11,252 --> 01:28:12,553
I just don't wanna be kept alive

1734
01:28:12,553 --> 01:28:14,455
on one of those
stinking machines.

1735
01:28:18,459 --> 01:28:20,194
I mean, it's my life, right?

1736
01:28:20,194 --> 01:28:21,763
And I think I'm the best judge

1737
01:28:21,763 --> 01:28:24,332
