when it's not over.

1738
01:28:28,836 --> 01:28:30,204
- Dad, there's something
that I wanna tell ya.

1739
01:28:30,204 --> 01:28:32,440
- What am I gonna do
with the little kids?

1740
01:28:35,610 --> 01:28:37,979
I got kids that are scared Mike.

1741
01:28:37,979 --> 01:28:41,249
- Dad, there's something
that I wanna tell you, okay?

1742
01:28:43,318 --> 01:28:45,320
I don't know where to start.

1743
01:28:45,320 --> 01:28:47,021
- Well maybe it's best
that you didn't start Son,

1744
01:28:47,021 --> 01:28:50,725
'cause I'm not feeling so
good out here after all.

1745
01:28:50,725 --> 01:28:52,193
I'm gonna go on inside.

1746
01:28:52,193 --> 01:28:54,095
- Dad, I have to say this!

1747
01:28:54,095 --> 01:28:55,163
Now listen to me!

1748
01:28:56,798 --> 01:28:57,832
- What is it Michael?

1749
01:28:59,334 --> 01:29:00,468
- You were right.

1750
01:29:01,836 --> 01:29:04,339
All along I wanted
you to be miserable.

1751
01:29:08,009 --> 01:29:09,977
But it's not because
I didn't love you.

1752
01:29:11,612 --> 01:29:14,916
'Cause I love you more than
anybody in this whole world.

1753
01:29:18,519 --> 01:29:21,522
I just, I wanted you to
realize that you made a mistake

1754
01:29:23,224 --> 01:29:24,492
and come back to us.

1755
01:29:29,964 --> 01:29:31,966
When I was a kid Dad,
you were the best.

1756
01:29:34,168 --> 01:29:37,705
You were the best.
(solemn music)

1757
01:29:37,705 --> 01:29:38,539
And I miss that.

1758
01:29:42,610 --> 01:29:43,678
So I'm sorry.

1759
01:29:47,448 --> 01:29:50,318
- Well I'm glad you got
that off your chest.

1760
01:29:50,318 --> 01:29:51,486
Son, I'm glad.

