01:32:37,952 --> 01:32:39,453
I'm really tired Michael.

1786
01:32:41,622 --> 01:32:43,224
I think I'm gonna get some rest.

1787
01:32:44,325 --> 01:32:45,426
Get a little sleep.

1788
01:32:47,128 --> 01:32:47,962
Sleep.

