01:33:56,497 --> 01:33:57,732
- [Michael] Get a real job!

1801
01:33:57,732 --> 01:34:00,301
For crying out loud, I'm a Dad!

1802
01:34:01,736 --> 01:34:04,171
- [Mike] It's been years
since my Father's passing.

1803
01:34:05,339 --> 01:34:07,174
I know now that he
loved me all along.

1804
01:34:08,943 --> 01:34:12,179
But as I reflect on my
own life and my Father's,

1805
01:34:12,179 --> 01:34:14,348
I realize that the
choices we make in life

1806
